div.div:
Important
: the path is preserverd throughout the chain. This means that the path from the behavior is also forwarded to the loadbalancer and from the loadbalancer to the container. Therefore the application in the container should be aware that it has a path prefix.
For example
: a request for the /auth endpoints will be routed trough the CloudFront behavior and to the loadbalancer the path still contains /auth so it will be mapped to the auth container. Inside the auth container the request still contains /auth so the application context must be available at the /auth path.
